products.title: Ascend Mat 4mm
products.body_html:
Professional-grade yoga mat built for serious flow and focused strength, made with SGS-certified natural rubber

✓ 100% natural rubber on both sides
✓ Dual-sided reversible grip
✓ Built to last, day after day

products.title: Mastery Mat 4mm
products.body_html:
Everyday yoga mat designed with unshakeable grip and lasting durability, made with SGS-certified natural rubber

✓ Grippy with even sweat palms
✓ High-density support for stability
✓ Move freely on this large mat

products.title: Away Travel Mat 1.5mm
products.body_html:
Lightweight, foldable yoga mat designed to let you bring your practice on the go, made with SGS-certified natural rubber

✓ Fit in your carry-on suitcase
✓ Grippy with even sweat palms
✓ Move freely on this large mat

products.title: Dual Flow Bundle
products.body_html: Two Mastery Mats so you and a partner can practice together with comfort and grip.

products.title: Travel Flow Bundle
products.body_html: Two Away Mats that are lightweight, foldable, and easy to pack for practice anywhere.

products.title: Complete Flow Bundle
products.body_html: One Mastery Mat and one Away Travel Mat, giving you the perfect balance of home stability and travel-ready freedom.

products.title: Elevate Flow Bundle
products.body_html: Two Ascend Mats built for performance and balance. Ideal for couples or advanced practitioners who want to rise higher together.
